DESCRIPTION: High Voltage Fairies in the Pit Every last Friday of the month the Fairy Pit opens up at Viper Room: Vienna’s only Metal & DnB Party! Grab your wings and boots and jump headfirst into the madness. ½ Entry in fairy costume! What to expect? Heavy guitar riffs and nasty bass drops. Free shots\, glow sticks & LED crowns. Celebrate the last weekend of pride with the Fairies!  One pit to rule them all: Alternative & Nu Metal\, Metalcore + Drum and Bass  with JD Dyslexia  Sounds Like: Electric Callboy | Linkin Park | Bring Me the Horizon | Pendulum | The Prodigy | Camo &amp\; Krooked | Zardonic | Motionless in White | Falling in Reverse | Enter Shikari | Bad Omens | Architects | I Prevail | Beartooth | Babymetal | Solence | The Qemists | System of a Down | Slipknot | Korn | Skindred | Avenged Sevenfold | A Day to Remember | We Came As Romans | Asking Alexandria | Pierce the Veil | Landmvrks | Parkway Drive | Ice Nine Kills | Three Days Grace | Breaking Benjamin | Bullet for My Valentine | My Chemical Romance | Sum 41 | Blink-182 | The Offspring | Papa Roach | Limp Bizkit | Hollywood Undead | Chase &amp\; Status | Sub Focus | Dimension | Delta Heavy | Kritikal | Luude | Circadian | Hedex | Sota | Noisia Goodies: Gratis Eintritts-Shots und High Voltage Fairies Party Vibes mit Knicklichtern & LED-Kronen Merch Stand: Schnapp dir High Voltage Fairies (HVF) Merch günstiger als online\, mit HVF-Merch bekommst du halben Eintritt bei unseren Events! Limited Online Presale: Early Bird Tickets: 7€ Abendkassa: Im Feen-Kostüm / HVF-Merch: 6€ | Standard: 10€  
